# FitPass AI — Phase 1

Welcome to the Phase 1 development of **FitPass AI**, a smart fitness tracking and recommendation system powered by artificial intelligence.

## 🚀 Project Overview

FitPass AI aims to revolutionize personal fitness by providing:
- Intelligent workout recommendations
- Real-time progress tracking
- Personalized fitness goals based on user data

This repository contains the foundational codebase for Phase 1, focusing on core architecture, data ingestion, and initial model development.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Python 3.10+
- FastAPI
- PostgreSQL
- Docker
- GitHub Actions (CI/CD)
- Machine Learning: scikit-learn, TensorFlow (planned)

## 📦 Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Renuka-0310/fitpass_ai_phase1.git
cd fitpass_ai_phase1
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # or venv\Scripts\activate on Windows
pip install -r requirements.txt
